text: James Bonnici (born January 21, 1972 in Omaha, Nebraska) also known as Jim is a former professional baseball player.https://www.baseball- reference.com/register/player.cgi?id=bonnic001jam At his highest level he played for the Orix Blue Wave in the Japan Pacific League.https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.cgi?id=bonnic001jam ==References== Category:Orix BlueWave players Category:Living people Category:1972 births Category:Sportspeople from Omaha, Nebraska
